{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "首輪競賽", "storyInfo": "第一輪找赤金比賽一開始，鼠膽龍威隊就遭到了其他隊伍的圍攻。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$fesedm_intro", "key": "$fesedm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的觀眾們，萬眾期待的第八屆多索雷斯極限鐵人大獎賽，即將正式開幕！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在開幕前，讓我們有請我們敬愛的坎黛拉市長發表開幕詞。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市民們，遊客們，歡迎來到我引以為豪的城市，多索雷斯！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論你來自哪裡，無論你有著怎麼樣的過去。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你能夠來到這座城市，那就都放下吧。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "享受這座城市帶給你的一切，享受你應該享受的一切吧。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高興起來，歡笑起來，尖叫起來。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是我為你們所有人打造的樂園！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#5"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，在這裡收獲你們一生中最難忘的時光吧！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，非常感謝坎黛拉市長一如既往點燃激情的開幕詞，那麼，接下來，我們來介紹各位參賽選手。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今年依舊有不少熟面孔，而且新面孔也不少！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先，看起來是一對恩愛情侶，實際上也是一對恩愛情侶，但是戰鬥力卻十分高的隊伍！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甜蜜夏日隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201", "name2": "avg_npc_202", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是愛的力量讓我們相遇。", "name": "急躁的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201", "name2": "avg_npc_202", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是愛的力量讓我們相愛。", "name": "懶散的女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201", "name2": "avg_npc_202", "focus": 0.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們兩個人愛的力量，是無敵的！", "name": "男遊客&女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛的力量如此閃耀，連我都要暈過去了！讓我們拭目以待愛的力量能夠走多遠吧！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後是單人成隊，來自大胃王海選的出線選手，水月！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外表人畜無害，卻吃掉了我們一家餐廳倉庫存量的食物，擁有著無底的胃袋以及與這片海洋相得益彰的藍色頭髮。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃豆人隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈囉哈囉，大家好呀。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#7"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "水月選手，有什麼振奮人心的參賽宣言嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#3"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......玩膩了就把你們都吃掉哦。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#3"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢噢噢，水月選手，用最平淡的口吻說出了最恐怖的話，讓我們期待他的活躍！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，是由本地人組成的隊，隊長拉菲艾拉小姐雖然外表可愛，卻拿著一把兇惡大鐮，這種反差正是這支隊伍的一大看點。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們歡迎——灰羽隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#7"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家好哦。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#7"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉菲艾拉小姐，你的參賽宣言是什麼？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#7"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我會努力的。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#7"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯嗯，好的，好的，有的時候，樸實無華才最動人！灰羽隊，我很看好你們！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著，是本次比賽的新面孔，卻也是最受矚目的一隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中途插入混戰海選，以無人能敵的姿態獲勝，得到了潘喬先生青睞的超新星。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由兩位來自雙日城友好城市——龍門的女俠，林雨霞小姐，陳暉潔小姐，以及本地的武器店老闆，埃內斯托先生組成的隊伍————", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "————鼠膽龍威隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又強又新的隊伍總是讓人欲罷不能，他們的賠率相當高，但是，你真的敢對他們下注嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，請隊長發表一下參賽宣言吧。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰是隊長？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托，你來吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正林雨霞不可能聽我的。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不可能聽我的。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，好吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我們的參賽宣言是——在這場比賽的歷史上刻下屬於我們的痕跡！", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，二位？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一般。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想也是。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常霸氣的宣言！讓我們期待鼠膽龍威隊的精彩表現。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，接下來的隊伍是......", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，Missy，這邊。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來了！喂，別擠，我的霜淇淋！", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是，人也太多了吧......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說明這場比賽萬眾矚目啊。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起這個，你快看，老陳居然拿著跟銃差不多的玩意兒。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來她這次是不打算用劍了啊。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她這不是作繭自縛嗎，她射擊訓練成績也就和我差不多吧。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，你不要把優秀說得和不要錢一樣好不好。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她劍術可不止是優秀的水準。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，Missy，我發現，你只要不當著老陳的面，誇起她來比我還過分啊。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在陳述事實好不好。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是是。不過，比起這個，老陳用劍以外的武器，這可是珍貴影像啊。等下去問問主辦方能不能要一份比賽錄影好了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別去了，丟死人了。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#3"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這有什麼丟人的，到時候剪成一部片，我名字都想好了，就叫《老陳用銃大顯神威》。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我發現你說不定有導演爛片的天賦。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過獎過獎。對了，Missy，跟您商量個事。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別啊，我還沒說什麼事呢。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一說您，我剛吃下去的霜淇淋都差點吐出來，你用這種語氣求人的時候肯定沒好事。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，不是，就，我看到他們官方有一個面向觀眾的節目。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看了看，可以猜誰會贏，還有很多小項目，比如誰最先搶到金塊，誰第一個出局什麼的，就......", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個猜字用得可真是精髓。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是官方項目，正規合法。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁，這座城市裡幹什麼違法？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這你倒是也沒說錯，不過我們現在畢竟只是旅客，管不了那麼多。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且你看，雖然你是想看老陳她們笑話，但是萬一她們要是贏了，我們也不虧對不對。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙贏啊，Missy。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉，算了，卡給你。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝詩大小姐。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別亂花啊！", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，以上就是全部四十支參賽隊伍。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比賽將全程用攝影機和無人機跟蹤拍攝，力求讓觀眾們不錯過任何一個精彩的鏡頭。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並且，除了這個主舞台之外，官方還分設了十個分舞台並配備了專門的主持人。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望能在不錯過精彩鏡頭的基礎上為各位觀眾帶來同樣精彩的解說。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，在開幕式開始的時間點，為了讓觀眾們也享受到參與比賽的樂趣，我們為觀眾們也準備了豐富多彩的競猜專案。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位觀眾在官方網站上登入自己的資訊後可以為自己賺一筆外快！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體操作流程請參照官方發佈的比賽指南。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，各位參賽選手現在已經在我們的出發區域準備就緒了。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一輪比賽，將在被劃分好的區域中進行赤金的尋找與爭奪，獲得赤金的隊伍可以直接交付給終點的工作人員。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，也可以嘗試奪取更多的赤金，因為，獲得的赤金就是屬於他們的！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，請坎黛拉市長拉響代表比賽開始的禮炮吧！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我宣佈——第一輪比賽，正式開始！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$fireworks"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼說？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "分頭行動。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在避免共同行動上，看來我們倒是很好達成共識。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，在那之前，看來已經有人盯上我們了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "陳一掃視，發現已經有十數個不懷好意的人從各個方向將他們三人圍住。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先突圍。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#6"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "林雨霞微微點頭。只見她的手在身邊房屋的玻璃窗上輕輕一抹，玻璃如同熔化了一般緩慢消失。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "而後，她的手中出現了一把鋒利的刀刃，這把刀刃幾近無色，只有反射陽光帶來的細微光芒證明著它確實存在。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢噢，第一輪一開始，本次大獎賽中備受期待的鼠膽龍威隊就被另外三支隊伍聯手盯上了！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙方的戰鬥一觸即發！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會是鼠膽龍威隊再一次向我們展現他們的實力，還是其他隊伍團結的勝利，讓我們拭目以待！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}